description: Mayfair Gold Corp., an exploration-stage company, acquires, explores, evaluates, and develops mineral properties. It holds a 100% interest in the Fenn-Gib gold project that covers an area of 4,800 hectares comprising 21 fee simple patented properties, 153 unpatented mining claims, and 144 patented leasehold mining claims located in the Guibord, Munro, Michaud, and McCool Townships in northeast Ontario, Canada. The company was incorporated in 2019 and is headquartered in Matheson, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Patrick Charles Evans B.A., B.Sc.
